@startuml
actor Staff
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "staff-service" as StaffService
participant "mobile-service" as MobileService
database "PostgreSQL Mobile DB" as MobileDB

Staff -> Gateway: POST /api/staff/mobiles/
Gateway -> StaffService: POST /staff/mobiles/
StaffService -> StaffService: Validate JWT staff
StaffService -> MobileService: POST /mobiles/
MobileService -> MobileDB: Insert mobile
MobileDB --> MobileService: Mobile row
MobileService --> StaffService: Created mobile
StaffService --> Gateway: Success response
Gateway --> Staff: Mobile created
@enduml
